 "html": "<p>Ek koop altyd Woolies se tamatiesop en dan kan ek my ophang aan dit.  Ek het vandag n tamatiesop gemaak wat so hap-hap aan die Woolies een.  Regtig baie lekker.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BROCCOLI-086.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1640\" alt=\"MARINDA BROCCOLI 086\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BROCCOLI-086-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>BENODIG:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1 ui</li>\n<li>3 knoffeltoontjies<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BROCCOLI-047.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1632\" alt=\"MARINDA BROCCOLI 047\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BROCCOLI-047-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>30 ml olyfolie</li>\n<li>30 ml komyn/jeera  die saadjies</li>\n<li>4 hoender of groente ekstrak blokkies<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BROCCOLI-049.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1633\" alt=\"MARINDA BROCCOLI 049\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BROCCOLI-049-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>750 ml kookwater</li>\n<li>2 blikkies kersietamaties</li>\n<li>1 blikkie tamatie puree<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BROCCOLI-053.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1635\" alt=\"MARINDA BROCCOLI 053\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BROCCOLI-053-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>30 ml suiker</li>\n<li>sout en peper na smaak</li>\n<li>250 ml room</li>\n</ul>\n<p>NOU:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>sny die ui in ringetjie en kap die knoffel fyn</li>\n<li>braai die ui, knoffel en komyn in die olyfolie net tot glaserig<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BROCCOLI-052.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1634\" alt=\"MARINDA BROCCOLI 052\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BROCCOLI-052-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>los die 4 ekstrakblokkies in die kookwater op</li>\n<li>gooi nou al die res van die bestandele behalwe die room by die uie in die pot<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BROCCOLI-058.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1636\" alt=\"MARINDA BROCCOLI 058\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BROCCOLI-058-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>kook vir 20 minute sonder deksel</li>\n<li>gebruik n voedselverwerker of n blenderstok en verpulp alles<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BROCCOLI-075.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1637\" alt=\"MARINDA BROCCOLI 075\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BROCCOLI-075-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>roer die room net voor opdiening by<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BROCCOLI-088.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1641\" alt=\"MARINDA BROCCOLI 088\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BROCCOLI-088-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Die sop is heerlik en kan met fyngekapte pietersielie, basiliekruidblare, bloukaas, feta of sommer net lekker brood bedien word.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BROCCOLI-094.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1638\" alt=\"MARINDA BROCCOLI 094\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BROCCOLI-094-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>",
